{"tid":2112542,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"跟進有關 Sony Android 8 機型無法連接問題","createTime":"2020-07-17T11:33:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T08:21:00.000Z","uid":179338,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1de0176be5315222ccb9008dbcc638854a66001c","tid":2112542,"uid":179338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:33:58.000Z","msg":"關於日前部分Android 機型<br />\n（主要為 Sony Xperia XA1, Android 8.0，及部分 Samsung 機型) <br />\n出現無法連接的問題，<br />\n問題已經修復，更新版本會暫時先於 Google Play Beta 推出，<br />\n稍後測試完成後會再推送到正式版<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />非常感謝連日來協助測試的用戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG Android Beta 申請方法： <br />\n前往： <a href=\"https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.lihkg.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fapps%2Ftesting%2Fcom.lihkg.app&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=dc792df5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/apps/testing/com.lihkg.app</a><br />\n然後點擊「成為測試人員」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再等多陣 就可以係 Google Play 接收到 Beta 更新架喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有其他Android 應用程式上的問題<br />\n歡迎留言、電郵到 info@lihkg.com 或Telegram到 <a href=\"http://t.me/LIHKGAndroid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLIHKGAndroid&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=044f9321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/LIHKGAndroid</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋會盡快處理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830b309de3219b79501038ff56be60bd9a42ecb1","tid":2112542,"uid":192776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6640edfea2215a902e39f77be323bd69940f15cd","tid":2112542,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e2321e095fa507f93ca08cb54f45f51795a0b8","tid":2112542,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"